testsuite.name: oradb::cleanpath With invalid parameters with wrong number of parameters

testcase.name: oradb::cleanpath With invalid parameters with wrong number of parameters should run oradb::cleanpath() and raise an ArgumentError with the message matching /expects 1 argument/
oradb::cleanpath With invalid parameters with wrong number of parameters should run oradb::cleanpath("a", "b") and raise an ArgumentError with the message matching /expects 1 argument/
